process

public void process(org.apache.uima.jcas.JCas arg0)
             throws org.apache.uima.analysis_engine.AnalysisEngineProcessException
Iterates through sentences and passes them to the HMM chunker, extracting gene mentions. From here, we will add them to the CAS' annotation list. Each gene mention will receive the DEFAULT_SCORE.
